channel.title: LaceNote - A New MMORPG
channel.description:
[size=24pt][font=georgia]LaceNote[/font][/size] The Development team thread can be found here: [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,493241.0.html]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,493241.0.html[/url] For immediate updates follow LaceNote on twitter: [url=http://twitter.com/#!/LaceNote]http://twitter.com/#!/LaceNote[/url]
This project will not use Runescape's client, our team will make our own emotions, objects, NPCS and items. Making this new MMORPG unable to be shut down due to copywrite.
[b]Current Staff:[/b] [b]Website Team:[/b] Lacenote[Head Developer of Website Team] Silverwaves[Moderator] [b]Java Devo Team[/b] pk2play[Head Developer of Java Devo Team] Lacenote[Head Developer of Java Devo Team] [b]Dream Team[/b] Loveandpower Uncalled Lacenote Qoodscape [b]Graphics Team[/b] //You can apply for this by messaging me or my email (lacenote@live.com) //This includes any of the following: Photoshop, 3D model creating, and Emotes
This is the development page for LaceNote... Pictures will get added once the client and the website has its final layout. The final layout of the website shouldn't take long though, I have created several pages with no CSS waiting to be added in, and soon will once I think of the best possible layout for a MMORPG website.
[b]**/---->Website Updates[/b] **All (*) are finished 95 + percent. ** [b]**/---->[/b] May 21, 2011 - Login(*) May 21, 2011 - Register(*) May 21, 2011 - Logout(*) May 21, 2011 - Hashing to Password//Creates .Java in char folder(*) May 21, 2011 - Profile Page(*) May 22, 2011 - Restricted words on register such as Mod and swears.(*) May 22, 2011 - Recovery Word(*) May 22, 2011 - Hashed Recovery Word(*) May 22, 2011 - Report a player(*) May 22, 2011 - Upgrade to members() May 22, 2011 - Itemdb(8 items so far) May 23, 2011 - Points(*) May 23, 2011 - Upgrade to members via points(*) May 23, 2011 - Messages from Staff () May 23, 2011 - Highscores() May 23, 2011 - Stripped all CSS from document until i come up with a good layout(*) May 24, 2011 - improved report system(*) May 24, 2011 - Appeal to a black mark() May 24, 2011 - improved upgrade(*) May 24, 2011 - Change current password(*) May 24, 2011 - Cleaned up Login code(*) May 24, 2011 - Added CSS back into the website for the layout(*) May 24, 2011 - Auto Profile Picture via what tribe your in () <- .01% May 24, 2011 - Re-done navigation(*) May 25, 2011 - Improved Navigation(*) May 25, 2011 - Updated ItemDB(*)
[code] Game Development May 25, 2011 - Blank Source! - created login/logout(*) May 25, 2011 - Created displays for each player right(*) May 25, 2011 - Created max level: 70() May 25, 2011 - Created level 70 exp: 20,000,001() May 25, 2011 - Max combat: 89() May 25, 2011 - Adding Vigor.() May 25, 2011 - Scaled hitting to size.() [/code] Started adding in the CSS to the website... (Release Soon!) [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/6rscg0.png[/img]
